title: Renee Zellweger pregnant in 'Bridget Jones's Baby' set photos
text:
*Los Angeles:* Following the first-look image of Renee Zellweger in 'Bridget Jones's Baby', some new photos from the set of the movie have arrived, in which the actress is pregnant.*Renee Zellweger. Pic/Santa Banta*
